com.example.bot.spring

Class ProjectUnknownController

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.bot.spring.ProjectUnknownController

  • public class ProjectUnknownController
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the controller used to handle unknown user text messages. The message will be recorded into the database for later review. Additional info including userId and the last 5 text messages s/he sent will be recorded for tracing. And all registered staff (by saying a passcode or injefting userId into database) will be notified immediately.

      • handleUnknown

        public void handleUnknown(java.lang.String userID,
                          java.lang.String fullQuestion,
                          java.lang.String[] questionArray)
        Method to handle unknown questions. This will record the question(String)+lsat 5 questions (String array) into the database Question table. A message will also be sent to all Staffs in Staff table.
        Parameters:
        userID - The sender if this text message.
        fullQuestion - The question that the chatbot couldn't handle.
        questionArray - Array of up to 5 text messages sent by the user.
